---
interface Props {
  packTypeLabel: string;
}

const { packTypeLabel } = Astro.props;

const sourceSteps = ['PDF 可搜索化', 'DeepTutor 出题', 'Excel 导出', '题域刷题'];
---

<section class="mt-8 space-y-6 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 p-6">
  <div>
    <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-blue-600">包类型</p>
    <p class="mt-1 text-base font-medium text-slate-900">{packTypeLabel}</p>
    <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-600">本站为只读预览，不判题、不记分；完整刷题与订阅请在 App 内完成。</p>
  </div>

  <div>
    <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-800">题域是什么？</p>
    <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-600">
      题域是 Android 刷题 App：导入 Excel 或订阅公开包后在本地练习；发现页可浏览共享题库，无需在网页刷题。
    </p>
  </div>

  <div>
    <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-800">App 内如何订阅？</p>
    <ol class="mt-2 list-decimal space-y-1 pl-5 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-600">
      <li>下载并打开题域 App（内测期见 <a href="/download" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700">下载页</a>）</li>
      <li>在「小组」页上半区「发现」浏览公开包，或从本分享页记住包名</li>
      <li>点击订阅，题目写入本地分类，即可开始刷题</li>
    </ol>
    <a href="/docs#subscribe-public-pack" class="mt-2 inline-block text-sm font-medium text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700">
      查看详细步骤 →
    </a>
  </div>

  <div>
    <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-800">题目从哪来？</p>
    <div class="mt-3 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2 text-xs text-slate-600">
      {
        sourceSteps.map((step, index) => (
          <span class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="rounded-full bg-white px-3 py-1 ring-1 ring-slate-200">{step}</span>
            {index < sourceSteps.length - 1 && <span class="text-slate-300">→</span>}
          </span>
        ))
      }
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
